	(gr_text "Why Weird is Wonderful (and Bankable)\n\n	Being weird means being noticeably \n	different. It means being or doing \n	something that makes other people \n	stare, or laugh, applaud, or boo. \n	And it's something we all need to \n	cultivate.\n\n				-- Forbes (2011)"
